In your app/assets/stylesheets, rename your application.css to application.scss
•Empty your application.scss(or just remove all *= require lines) and put the following:
@import ‘bootstrap-sprockets’;
@import ‘bootstrap’;
•In app/assets/javascript, add:
//= require bootstrap-sprockets

In your Gemfile, add the following:
gem ‘bootstrap-sass’
gem ‘simple_form’
•In command line: bundle install
•In command line: rails generate simple_form:install--bootstrap